{"tid":1723284,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"Cheng Lap：由六月開始 我哋都賭緊showhand","createTime":"2019-11-15T06:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T08:04:01.000Z","uid":24814,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"772a13351f28e048b71bdbd6e9c6d6e2c5321249","tid":1723284,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:54:30.000Z","msg":"算了, 我還是說吧.<br />\n<br />\n打從六月開始, 去到七月, 這個抗爭就是一場 showhand, 玩過沙蟹嗎? 政府跟市民, 都是不斷加注的. showhand 這遊戲, 是沒得回頭的, 也不會像賭聖一樣, 投降輸一半, 結果一定是勝者全拿, 敗者一無所有.<br />\n<br />\n而玩下去就要加注. 只看哪一方到最後是二仔底, 就要全輸, 或者本來會贏的一方, 因為失去信心, 而自己縮了, 由贏變輸.<br />\n<br />\n沒有中間, 輸就是停損位, 停損的人也是輸, 他只是不用再加注而已.<br />\n<br />\n這麼簡單的遊戲, 就不要再有甚麼僥倖了, 如果你不打算加注, 不覺得會贏, 你一開始又為何要玩這遊戲?"},{"pid":"8ac42d3dce94a18239f0555ad244b594dd546e3e","tid":1723284,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:58:18.000Z","msg":"比喻好好"},{"pid":"0b9b3cc8fabc11efe85ebab00a3658a7d97d075b","tid":1723284,"uid":332860,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:01:48.000Z","msg":"今次輸 唔係輸十年 係輸撚晒"},{"pid":"de4adf5eaf75d84f2055b10087d11ad0f253b5ce","tid":1723284,"uid":31637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b9b3cc8fabc11efe85ebab00a3658a7d97d075b","tid":1723284,"uid":332860,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:01:48.000Z","msg":"今次輸 唔係輸十年 係輸撚晒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:05:48.000Z","msg":"知就好啦<br />\n咁仲係度柒下柒下血債物償, 就住就住?"},{"pid":"3e67fafa9b14ff89bce20de0105ac1a0f847fc35","tid":1723284,"uid":29188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:50:54.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，一步不能讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c6909d85d86afee66691593d8946fafa68b17f","tid":1723284,"uid":67813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:54:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"996d8368f30b85cedc113c3c1e154f8c0108b5b0","tid":1723284,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime